        </item>
        <item>
            <title>日本麦当劳推出「薯条加湿器」 散发薯条香气</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/17/mcdonaldsjapan/shop_guide/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mcdonaldsjapan</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/17/mcdonaldsjapan/shop_guide/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 03:07:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[买物情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[日本麦当劳]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[薯条加湿器]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[麦当劳]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210096</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">日本麦当劳推出 2024 年福袋，当中最触目是号称使用后可令房间充满薯条味的「薯条加湿器」。消息推出后，即时引来网民讨论。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr">2024 年の福袋は「BRUNO」とコラボ🐧✨<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E3%83%9E%E3%82%AF%E3%83%89%E3%83%8A%E3%83%AB%E3%83%89%E3%81%AE%E7%A6%8F%E8%A2%8B2024?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#マクドナルドの福袋 2024</a> 事前抽选贩売応募受付中❗<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BRUNO%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E3%82%B3%E3%83%A9%E3%83%9C%E3%82%A2%E3%82%A4%E3%83%86%E3%83%A0?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#BRUNO 限定コラボアイテム</a> と <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E7%84%A1%E6%96%99%E5%88%B8?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#商品无料券</a> をゲットしよう❗</p><p>チャーミングな「ポテト加湿器」や、BRUNOならではのおしゃれなアイテムがたくさん❗<br />さらに10 人に1 人、金のマックカードが当たるチャンスも❗</p><p>&mdash; マクドナルド (@McDonaldsJapan) <a href="https://twitter.com/McDonaldsJapan/status/1734400176943440287?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 12, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">是次推出的麦当劳 2024 年福袋是与日本生活品牌 BRUNO 联名合作，加湿器外型是经典的红色包装和金黄薯条，其中一个卖点是加湿器会散发薯条香气。要获得薯条加湿器，需要在 12 月 19 日前，在日本 McDonald’s App 申请抽奖资格。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1210100 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/05-8.png" alt="" width="490" height="490" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/05-8.png 490w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/05-8-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲薯条加湿器</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">除了薯条加湿器外，福袋里还有毯子、零钱包、迷你盘子及大量餐点免费兑换券，包括武士汉堡（炙烧酱油双层牛肉）、照烧汉堡、苹果派、OREO 巧克力冰沙、研磨咖啡等，总价值高达 3,430 日圆。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1210104 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/09.png" alt="" width="490" height="490" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/09.png 490w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/09-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲毯子</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1210101 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/07.png" alt="" width="490" height="490" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/07.png 490w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/07-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲零钱包</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1210103 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/08.png" alt="" width="490" height="490" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/08.png 490w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/08-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲迷你盘子</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.mcdonalds.co.jp/campaign/lb-2024-r57a0/?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=cpe&amp;utm_campaign=luckybag-2024&amp;utm_term=promo-tweet&amp;af_prt=dentsudigital">McDonaldsJapan</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/17/mcdonaldsjapan/shop_guide/">日本麦当劳推出「薯条加湿器」 散发薯条香气</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
